data.description: Light, bright and open! Gorgeous kitchen with white cabinetry, granite counters, stainless steel appliances and center island! Spacious living room with newer carpet (12/22) and walk-out to the deck. 2 bedrooms on the upper level including the primary suite w/walk-in closet and private bath featuring a soaking tub, separate shower and dual sinks. Convenient upper level laundry. Fabulous lower level storage room. Large maintenance free deck for grilling/entertaining. 2 car garage. Walking distance to parks, restaurants, library and downtown Lakeville. 194 schools! Rentals are allowed.
